---
description: Rules for Vasily templates/rundowns/integrations tasks
globs:
  - "frontend/src/features/templates/**"
  - "frontend/src/features/rundowns/**"
  - "frontend/src/features/control/**"
  - "frontend/src/pages/TemplatesPage.tsx"
  - "frontend/src/pages/ControlPage.tsx"
  - "backend/src/routes/templates.ts"
  - "backend/src/routes/rundowns.ts"
  - "backend/src/routes/channels.ts"
  - "backend/src/services/templates/**"
  - "backend/src/services/rundowns/**"
  - "backend/src/integrations/**"
---

You are working in Vasily ownership: templates DB, rundowns, channels, and external integrations.

Allowed by default:

- templates/rundowns/channels backend routes and services;
- templates/rundowns/control frontend feature modules;
- Dalet or other integration adapters.

Ask before changing:

- editor internals;
- renderer/timeline engine;
- LLM generation pipeline;
- `decklink-out/**`;
- shared schemas unless the task is explicitly about contracts.

Keep external integrations behind adapters under `backend/src/integrations/**`.
